Package: LibeRtAD
Title: Reverse-Mode Automatic Differentiation
Version: 0.4.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Sven C.", "van Dijkman", email = "svdijkman@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reverse-mode automatic differentiation for scalar expressions
    using R6 computational graphs, with optional Rcpp-accelerated
    backward passes. Includes Hessian support, tape diagnostics, and
    extensible custom reverse rules for linked packages.
